        complex ideas into accessible, beautiful, and functional products that
        delight users and drive business success.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have had the privilege of working on a diverse range of projects
        across different industries, which has given me a broad perspective and
        a versatile skill set. My design philosophy is rooted in empathy and
        innovation, always striving to understand the user's needs and pushing
        the boundaries of whatâ€™s possible.
      </p>
      <p>
        Some of the work I'm proud of:
        <ul>
          <li>
            Building a school management app at <a
              class="highlight"
              href="/work#new-visions-for-public-schools"
              >New Visions for Public Schools</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Designing climate tech solutions at <a
              class="highlight"
              href="/work#upstream-tech">Upstream Teach</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Developing a customer support chatbot at <a
              href="/work#sage-talk"
              class="highlight">SageAI</a
